cs.NA, cs.CE, cs.MS, cs.DC, cs.SY 

Reasoning: 
- cs.NA (Numerical Analysis): The paper discusses solving ill-posed inverse problems using numerical methods and presents a software package for the same. 
- cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science): The paper discusses applications of the proposed software package in geophysical imaging, which falls under the purview of computational engineering. 
- cs.MS (Mathematical Software): The paper presents a software package for solving PDE parameter estimation problems, which falls under the category of mathematical software. 
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing): The paper discusses novel parallelization schemes for solving parameter estimation problems with many measurements, which falls under the purview of distributed and parallel computing. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses solving multiphysics inversion problems, which can be seen as a control problem, and presents a software package for the same.
